<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.276530>
    dc:description "FIGURES 58 – 63. Fenestrulina ampla Canu & Bassler, 1928 a. 58 – 60, USNM 8560 (holotype specimen of Fenestrulina ampla), Rio de Janeiro, Brazil. 58 – 59, Colony with autozooids and one ovicelled zooid; 60, close-up of orifice with three oral spines. 61 – 63, MZUSP 0 308 (part of specimen), off São Paulo, Brazil. 61, Colony; 62, close-up of ovicelled zooid; 63, close-up of autozooid." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/276530/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

